Firaministan India zai halarci aikin gina ginin haikalin a wurin da ake takaddama
NEW DELHI (AP) - Firayim Ministan Indiya Narendra Modi zai halarci wani bikin gina haikalin Hindu a watan gobe a wani wuri mai cike da takaddama a arewacin Indiya inda masu tsattsauran ra'ayin Hindu suka rushe wani masallaci na karni na 16 a shekarar 1992, a cewar amintaccen wanda ke kula da ginin haikalin.
An shirya bikin ne a ranar 5 ga watan Agusta, wanda masu shirya taron suka ce ya kasance mai kyau ga masu bin addinin Hindu amma kuma hakan yana nuna shekara guda tun lokacin da Majalisar Dokokin Indiya ta soke matsayin da ke da ikon mallakar jihar Jammu da Kashmir.
Alamar ba ta yiwuwa a rasa duka masu goyon baya da abokan adawar jam'iyyar Bharatiya Janata Party, ko BJP, ta Modi, wanda ke da ra'ayin wariyar launin fata na Hindu, wanda ya kwashe shekaru da dama yana da alkawuran da suka hada da alkawuran da suka hada da 'yancin kai na Kashmir da kuma gina haikalin ga allahn Hindu Ram inda masallacin Mughal ya kasance, wani wuri a birnin Ayodhya a jihar Uttar Pradesh wanda masu ibada suka yi imani da cewa shi ne wurin haifuwar Ram.
Saboda cutar coronavirus har yanzu tana ci gaba da yaduwa a Indiya, wacce ta ba da rahoton na uku mafi girma a duniya, za a watsa bikin kai tsaye a gidan talabijin na jihar kuma za a iyakance adadin mahalarta da masu kallo, a cewar Vishwa Hindu Parishad, ko Kungiyar Hindu ta Duniya, ƙungiyar 'yan kishin Hindu da ke da alaƙa da BJP.
Haikalin zai zama "cibiyar ci gaba da rashin mutuwa na jituwa ta zamantakewa, hadin kai da haɗin kai na ƙasa da farkawar Hindutva, " ko kuma hanyar rayuwar Hindu, in ji mai magana da yawun kungiyar Vinod Bansal a cikin sanarwar manema labarai a ranar Asabar.
An warware takaddamar da aka yi a tsawon karni a kan shafin a shekarar da ta gabata bayan nasarar zaben BJP.
