Tsaro mai tsaro a wajen ofishin jakadancin Amurka a Chengdu, China
Akwai tsauraran matakan tsaro a wajen ofishin jakadancin Amurka a birnin Chengdu, China a ranar Lahadi, yayin da ma'aikatan Amurka ke shirin barin ofishin.
An ga manyan motoci uku da ke motsawa suna shiga ginin ginin, yayin da 'yan sanda da ke cikin tufafi da' yan sanda suka yi layi a bangarorin biyu na titi, wanda aka kewaye da shingen karfe.
Editan jaridar Global Times ta kasar Sin ya wallafa cewa an ba wa ofishin jakadancin Amurka a Chengdu sa'o'i 72 don rufewa, ko har zuwa karfe 10 na safe (0200 GMT) Litinin, 27 ga Yuli.
China ta zargi cewa wasu ma'aikata a ofishin jakadancin na Chengdu suna "yin ayyukan da ba su dace da asalinsu ba".
Ba tare da bada wani bayani ba, kakakin ma'aikatar harkokin wajen kasar Sin, Wang Wenbin ya ce irin wannan aikin ya tsoma baki a harkokin kasar Sin kuma ya cutar da bukatun tsaro.
An bayar da umarnin rufe ofishin jakadancin China a Chengdu a ranar Juma'a a matsayin ramuwar gayya ga umarnin Amurka na rufe ofishin jakadancin China a Houston, Texas.
Washington ta umarci China da ta rufe ofishin Houston "don kare dukiyar Amurka da bayanan sirri na Amurka".
Yayin da aka rufe ofishin jakadancin kasar Sin a Houston a ranar Juma'a, an ga wasu mutane da suka bayyana a matsayin jami'an Amurka suna kutsawa cikin ginin ta wata kofa ta baya.
Wang ya ce a ranar Asabar cewa ya saba wa yarjejeniyar kasa da kasa da na kasashen biyu kuma China za ta mayar da martani, ba tare da tantance yadda ba.
Rufe-rufe na tit-tat ya kara hauhawar tashin hankali tsakanin kasashen biyu kan batutuwan daga cinikayya da leken asiri na masana'antu zuwa hakkin dan adam.
Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta ce dubban 'yan ta'addan da ke adawa da Pakistan a Afghanistan
ISLAMABAD -- Rahoton Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ya ce fiye da 'yan tawayen Pakistan 6,000 ne ke boye a Afghanistan, mafi yawansu na kungiyar Taliban ta Pakistan da aka haramta, wadanda ke da alhakin kai wa sojin Pakistan da fararen hula hari.
Rahoton da aka fitar a wannan makon ya ce kungiyar, da aka sani da Tehreek-e-Taliban (TTP), ta yi cudanya da kungiyar IS da ke da hedikwata a Afghanistan.
Wasu daga cikin 'yan kungiyar TTP har ma sun shiga kungiyar IS, wacce ke da hedikwatarta a gabashin Afghanistan.
Gwamnatin Afghanistan ba ta amsa ba a ranar Lahadi ga bukatar da kamfanin dillancin labarai na Associated Press ya yi na yin tsokaci.
