Landray ya ce wannan gazawar ta kasance mai ban haushi musamman idan ya zo ga amfani da plasma mai warkarwa, wanda likitoci da yawa suka yi imanin zai iya taka muhimmiyar rawa wajen kula da marasa lafiya masu cutar COVID-19.
"Idan ka duba Amurka, an yi amfani da adadi mai yawa na wannan magani bisa son rai da kuma son rai. Birtaniya ta fi fice fiye da yadda aka kwatanta da abin da ke faruwa a can", in ji shi.
Farfesa Peter Horby, masanin cututtuka masu yaduwa kuma wanda ya kafa shirin dawowa, ya ce: "Akwai rahotannin marasa lafiya 20,000 da ke samun plasma a cikin rukuni amma babu wani daga cikin waɗannan marasa lafiya da aka zaɓa.
