Magajin garin Kansas City ya yi maraba da taimakon tarayya wajen warware kisan kai, amma ya damu da dalilan Trump
Magajin garin Kansas City Quinton Lucas ya yi tambaya a ranar Lahadi dalilin Shugaba Trump na aikawa da jami'an tarayya zuwa garuruwan Amurka - yana mai cewa yayin da zai yi maraba da taimako wajen warware wasu kisan kai a cikin garin Midwestern, yana ganin matakin zai iya zama mafi game da sake zabar Trump.
"Na yi matukar takaici a wannan makon [cewa] shugaban ya ambaci zanga-zangar George Floyd, ya ambaci motsi na Black Lives Matter", in ji Lucas, ɗan Democrat, a kan "Fox News Sunday" na zanga-zangar kwanan nan game da rashin daidaito na launin fata da kuma zaluncin 'yan sanda.
"Ba haka yake a Kansas City ba. Mun samu ƙaruwa shekara shekara [amma] abin da muke bukatar taimako a kai shi ne ainihin warware wasu kashe-kashen da ba a warware ba".
Lucas ya kara da cewa: "Bari mu yi kokarin mayar da hankali kan warware kisan kai... Ina ganin idan ka saurari bayanan da aka yi kwanan nan... muna farin cikin yin aiki tare da jami'an tarayya a cikin iyaka".
Duk da sonsa na sanya jami'an tarayya su yi aiki tare da tilasta bin doka na gida, Lucas ya ce maganganun Trump - musamman dangane da rikice-rikicen da ke kewaye da dabarun da jami'an tarayya ke amfani da shi a Portland, Ore., - ya sa da yawa daga cikin masu zaɓe ya nuna damuwa game da kasancewar jami'an a titunan birni.
"Abin da ba mu buƙata ba shi ne ƙarin man fetur a kan wuta daga jami'an tarayya don yin, ina tsammanin, batun siyasa mai ban sha'awa", in ji shi.
Trump a ranar Laraba ya sanar da cewa yana tura jami'an tarayya 100 zuwa Chicago don taimakawa wajen magance karuwar yawan aikata laifuka - wani mataki wanda ke nuna fadada tsoma bakin fadar White House a cikin tilasta bin doka a cikin gida yayin da Trump ke ci gaba da sanya kansa a matsayin shugaban "doka da oda".
"Tashin" wakilan da aka sanar a ranar Laraba zuwa Chicago da sauran biranen Amurka na daga cikin aikin Legend - wanda aka kira shi bayan LeGend Taliferro mai shekaru 4 da haihuwa, wanda aka harbe shi har lahira yayin da yake barci a cikin wani gida a Kansas City a ƙarshen watan da ya gabata.
Duk da yake aikawa da jami'an tarayya don taimakawa tilasta yin doka a gida ba abin da ba a taɓa gani ba - Babban Lauyan Bill Barr ya ba da sanarwar irin wannan yunƙurin a watan Disamba don birane bakwai da suka ga tashin hankali - irin jami'an tarayya da aka aika, da kuma wasu daga cikin dabarun su, sun haifar da damuwa tsakanin jihohi da 'yan majalisa na gida.
Da dama daga cikin 'yan majalisa daga New York zuwa Portland sun yi magana a kan gwamnatin Trump ta tura jami'an zuwa garuruwan su, musamman bayan rahotannin da suka ce jami'an tarayya da ba a san su ba sun kama masu zanga-zanga a Portland kuma sun dauke su a cikin motocin da ba a san su ba.
An yi zanga-zangar kusan kowace rana a Portland a kan zaluncin 'yan sanda da wariyar launin fata tun bayan mutuwar George Floyd yayin da yake tsare a hannun 'yan sanda a Minneapolis a ranar 25 ga Mayu.
