Trump ya wallafa a shafinsa na Twitter cewa an yi wa kallon talabijin na NASCAR rauni ta hanyar zargin karya na aikata laifuka na kiyayya ga direban Bubba Wallace da kuma shawarar da ta yanke na hana nuna tutar Tarayyar a wasannin da take gudanarwa.
Kamar yadda ake tsammani, yawancin tambayoyin sun kasance game da tweet a matsayin mai ba da rahoto bayan mai ba da rahoto ya tambayi McEnany tambayoyin da aka tsara don sa ta ce Trump yana goyon bayan tutar Confederate.
