Ga Kianzad, mai shekaru 28, dan asalin Iran, nasara ce ta biyu a kan juyawa bayan nasarar da ta yi a kan Jessica-Rose Clark a UFC Fight Night a Moscow a watan Nuwamba.
Kianzad yanzu yana da 13-5 gaba daya kuma 2-1 a UFC, kamar yadda matar da aka sani da 'Banzai' ke da burin sauya matsayin 135lbs.
