Manyan kamfanonin tallace-tallace suna turawa ga masu saukar da farashi daga filayen jiragen sama, majalisun
Kafofin watsa labarai sun tara jari a farkon wannan shekarar don samar da ƙarin tabbacin kuɗi yayin da cutar ta fara tsoratar da masu talla.
Majiyoyi sun ce kamfanonin suna tattaunawa kan hanyoyin da za su iya rage yawan kudaden da suke samu ta hanyar rage haya ga wuraren da suke aiki ko kuma ta hanyar cirewa ko ragewa na mafi karancin kudin shiga, wanda aka saba gabatar da shi lokacin da aka fara sanya hannu kan yarjejeniya.
Wata majiya ta nuna cewa manyan kamfanonin tallan tallace-tallace na iya tabbatar da kashi 85 cikin ɗari na kudaden shiga da suke tsammani a cikin haya.
Wasu kwangila suna da sassan da ke ba su damar rage mafi ƙarancin garanti idan yawan mutane a wani yanki ya ragu da wani kashi, amma ba a bayyana ko wannan yanayin yana cikin kowane kwangila na yanzu tsakanin kamfanonin allon talla da masu ba da gidaje ba.
A lokaci guda, kamfanonin suna ba da rangwamen kuɗi ga masu talla don su cika wuraren da ke akwai a allon talla kuma su ba su mafi yawan kuɗi da kuɗi.
Allon talla a cikin Sydney CBD da kuma kewayen yankunan da ke waje waɗanda yawanci suna ɗaukar tallan tallace-tallace shida suna gwagwarmaya don cika dukkan wuraren da suke akwai.
Amma wasu shafuka - kamar su Ooh! kafofin watsa labarai's 40 x 10 mita talla a Sydney Airport - an inganta.
Oh Media ta ki yin sharhi, amma a wani taron Macquarie Australia a watan Mayu, ta yi nuni da sama da dala miliyan 20 a cikin tsayayyen kudin haya.
JC Decaux ya ki yin tsokaci.
Filin jirgin sama da kuma sufurin jama'a su ne kwangilar talla mai riba ga kamfanonin talla.
Dangane da Rahoton Ƙungiyar Ƙungiyar Ƙungiyar Ƙasa ta 2019, kudaden shiga daga sufuri - ciki har da filayen jiragen sama - ya kasance dala miliyan 169.4 yayin da kudaden shiga daga kayan ado na titi da kuma waje na bas da trams ya kasance dala miliyan 266.5.
Kasuwancin JC Decaux yana da kwangila tare da Filin jirgin saman Sydney, Yarra Trams, Filin jirgin saman Perth da kuma Sydney Buses. Oh! Media yana da allunan talla a yankuna kamar su Qantas lounges, a waje da filin jirgin saman Sydney, Filin jirgin saman Adelaide, Filin jirgin saman Darwin da tashoshin jirgin kasa a Sydney da Melbourne.
An gudanar da gwanjo don filin jirgin saman Melbourne da jiragen kasa na Sydney a lokacin annobar kuma ba a yanke shawara a hukumance ba.
Melbourne ita ce ta biyu mafi girma a filin jirgin sama a Australia kuma kafin coronavirus yana da darajar miliyoyin miliyoyin kowace shekara.
A sakamakon shekara a watan Fabrairu, oOh! Media ya ce ya samar da dala miliyan 65.9 daga rukunin 'fly', wanda galibi ya ƙunshi kudaden shiga daga Filin jirgin saman Sydney.
Kudaden da aka samu daga 'tafiya,' wanda ya kunshi kwangilar jirgin kasa da kayan titi da Adshel ya mallaka kafin a siya ta Oh!, ya kai dala miliyan 234.8.
