Motar ta shiga cikin taron, an harbi mai zanga-zangar a Colorado
AURORA, Colo. (AP) - Mota ta shiga cikin taron jama'a kuma an harbi mai zanga-zanga a cikin unguwar Denver da ke ke Aurora a lokacin zanga-zangar adawa da rashin adalci.
Hukumar 'yan sanda ta Aurora ta ce a shafin Twitter cewa masu zanga-zanga suna tafiya a kan Interstate 225 a ranar Asabar lokacin da wata mota ta wuce.
'Yan sanda sun ce wani mai zanga-zanga ya harba bindiga, inda ya kashe akalla mutum daya wanda aka kai shi asibiti a cikin yanayi mai kyau.
Hukumomi sun ce an ja motar kuma suna gudanar da bincike.
Masu zanga-zangar sun kuma fasa tagogi zuwa kotun kuma an fara wuta a ofishin, in ji 'yan sanda.
An ayyana taron ba bisa ka'ida ba kuma 'yan sanda sun umarci masu zanga-zangar su bar yankin, in ji hukumomi.
An kara tashin hankali a zanga-zangar da aka yi a baya-bayan nan kan rashin adalci na launin fata tun lokacin da aka tura jami'an tarayya don murkushe zanga-zangar a Portland, Oregon.
'Yan sanda sun ayyana wani tashin hankali a Seattle a ranar Asabar.
Zanga-zangar da aka yi a ranar 25 ga Mayu, mutuwar George Floyd, wani baƙar fata a Minnesota wanda ya mutu bayan wani jami'in farar fata ya riƙe shi a ƙasa tare da gwiwa a wuyansa, ya kuma nuna wasu lokuta na mummunan tashin hankali na 'yan sanda.
A Colorado, masu zanga-zanga sun jawo hankali ga mutuwar Elijah McClain, wanda 'yan sanda suka tsayar da shi yayin da yake tafiya a kan titin Aurora a watan Agusta 2019 bayan da wani mai kiran 911 ya ba da rahoton cewa yana da shakku.
'Yan sanda suka riƙe shi a wuyan hannu, kuma likitocin suka yi masa maganin ketamine, wanda ya kai miligram 500, don ya huce.
