Duk da haka wannan wasan kwaikwayo na National Theater of Greece ya saki sautin iska mai ƙarfi da fushi.
A lokacin da ya yi tsayi, wasan kwaikwayon ya yi kama da bugun jini a cikin hasken rana, yana ɗaukar numfashin ku - tasirin yana da ɗan kaɗan ta hanyar kallon kan layi.
Da farko an buga shi a cikin 472 KZ, "The Persians" na Aeschylus an dauke shi mafi tsufa wasan kwaikwayo na Girka.
An watsa wannan wasan kwaikwayon na Dimitris Lignadis kai tsaye a ranar Asabar daga tsohuwar wasan kwaikwayo na Epidaurus; a cikin ruhun wasan kwaikwayo, babu rikodin da ke kan layi.
An fara tunanin wurin ne a matsayin wani ɓangare na birnin asclepeion (cibiyar warkarwa) saboda Helenawa suna ganin daidaito tsakanin jiki da ruhu yana da muhimmanci ga lafiya mai kyau.
