Nunin ya shafi bayan Salamis, yaƙin na teku wanda Girkawa da suka fi rinjaye sun kori sojojin Farisa masu iko shekaru 2,500 da suka gabata.
A lokacin da sararin samaniya ke kusa, yana da matukar damuwa don shiga cikin masu sauraro na rayuwa don kallon 'yan wasan kwaikwayo (subtitled) a duk hanyar a Girka yayin da suke yin wasan kwaikwayo na shekaru dubu.
Aeschylus da kansa ya yi yaƙi a Salamis, amma wasan nasa yana da juzu'i: wannan tsohon soja na gefen nasara ya kafa labarinsa a tsakanin waɗanda aka ci nasara, yana mai da hankali sosai ga wahalar abokan gabansa na kwanan nan.
Maza 'yan Farisa, sanye da dogon rigar da aka yi da ruwan ruwan tan da kuma rigar da aka saka da farar riga, suka soma taron.
Suna cikin babban biransu suna jiran labari daga sarkinsu, Xerxes, wanda yake neman yaƙi da Athens.
Shigar da mahaifiyar gwauruwa ta Xerxes, Sarauniya Atossa (Lydia Koniordou), a cikin babban babban rigar baƙar fata wanda ya bayyana ta sa ta, maimakon akasin haka; ita mutum ce a cikin wani exoskeleton na masana'anta, duka mai rauni da ban tsoro.
Koniordou, wacce ke cikin manyan 'yan wasan kwaikwayo na Girka, ta san rawar da ke ciki - ta jagoranci kuma ta yi fim a cikin wani wasan kwaikwayo na farko na National Theater of Greece na "The Persians" wanda ya buga Cibiyar Birnin New York a shekara ta 2006 - kuma ta kafa matakan ba tare da yin komai ba.
A mafi yawancin lokuta, tana tsaye a tsakiyar filin wasan zagaye, ba tare da wata matsala ba ta nuna fushin da ke ƙonewa da baƙin ciki mai raɗaɗi yayin da aka bayyana girman bala'in da ya faru da sojojin gida.
An tabbatar da damuwar da kowa ke ji, a cikin cikakkun bayanai, ta hanyar manzo (Argyris Pandazaras) da ya dawo daga gaba.
A cikin wani abin mamaki, ya ba da labarin yaƙin, yana bugun kansa cikin hauka yayin da mambobin ƙungiyar mawaƙa ke rawa a kusa da shi kuma Giorgos Poulios ya yi rawar gani kamar yadda ya kamata ya zama abin da ya kamata ya zama matakin ji.
